Package edu.northwestern.at.utils.math.distributions

package edu.northwestern.at.utils.math.distributions

Methods for computing point probabilities and percentage points of common statistical distributions. The distributions include:

  • Normal distribution
  • Gaussian error distribution
  • Complete and incomplete beta distribution
  • Complete and incomplete gamma distribution
  • Student's t distribution
  • Fisher's F distribution
  • Chi-square distribution
